name: Pain
title: Pain
description: "This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024."
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values reflect patients experiencing pain, a localized or generalized uncomfortable sensations in the body.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this value set is to identify patients experiencing Pain.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes Pain related SNOMED CT codes from Findings hierarchy.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes Pain related SNOMED CT codes from Disorder of body system (disorder) hierarchy.)
